Falyanžur Al-'Insānu Mimma Khuliqa.
Khuliqa Min Mā'in Dāfiqin.
Yakhruju Min Bayni Aş-Şulbi Wa At-Tarā'ibi.
'Innahu `Alaá Raj`ihi Laqādirun.
Yawma Tublaá As-Sarā'iru.
Famā Lahu Min Qūwatin Wa Lā Nāşirin.
